{"tid":126141,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[出讓]想學衝浪必備良品 衝浪滑板Smoothstar","createTime":"2017-02-19T06:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T03:53:47.000Z","uid":86014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc12a371343dab03bbe52325cbf3c66ab9ab0e51","tid":126141,"uid":86014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"先介紹一下Smoothstar滑板, Smoothstar 是款模擬衝浪動作的滑板，它給了個穩定的狀態, 讓衝浪者可以不受浪況影響, 在板上衝浪的正確姿勢和動作，例如站板時雙腳的距離，不同於一般滑板，Smoothstar獨有設計可讓衝浪者在陸地上練習衝浪的tricks, 如air reverse 或cut back等等, 最適合是香港人多浪點少，一個浪幾個人搶著追，新手好少機會練習的環境。<br />\n<br />\n可以再看一下影片<br />\n官方的介紹<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v-2Gafv7qtI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv-2Gafv7qtI&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4ae32a24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v-2Gafv7qtI</a><br />\n<br />\n張震嶽 -沒有艷陽天也可以happy之沒有水也要衝浪。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4E1e0TJo-gY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4E1e0TJo-gY&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e187a3e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4E1e0TJo-gY</a><br />\n<br />\nNobody around - Smoothstar Skateboards <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YDxNJ0slB5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYDxNJ0slB5g&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b1e342c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YDxNJ0slB5g</a><br />\n<br />\n根據身高體重，Smoothstar有不同建議的滑板型號<br />\n我的是 Skateboards SMOOTHSTAR Johanne DEFAY 32.5&quot;<br />\n是和法國衝浪者 Johanne DEFAY 合作推出的型號，<br />\n適合身高160cm &ndash; 181cm (5&Prime;3&prime; &ndash; 5&Prime;11&prime;)     體重55kg &ndash; 95kg衝浪者<br />\n詳情可以看<a href=\"https://smoothstar.com.au/shop/complete-smoothstars/32-5%E2%80%B3-johanne-defay-pro-model-aquagrey/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsmoothstar.com.au%2Fshop%2Fcomplete-smoothstars%2F32-5%25E2%2580%25B3-johanne-defay-pro-model-aquagrey%2F&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d09d6dc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://smoothstar.com.au/shop/complete-smoothstars/32-5%E2%80%B3-johanne-defay-pro-model-aquagrey/</a><br />\n<br />\n我的滑板在台灣買的(HKD 2000)，買回來只玩過幾次 (95%新)<br />\n 因為工作忙，沒時間練習，所以出讓，如果有衝浪者或其他有意接觸衝浪運動的人有興趣，或想了解更多，歡迎PM聯絡我"},{"pid":"d50aa873c72252bf0a920d6619bda203f57bddd0","tid":126141,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T02:17:14.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"25fb911e4fee2a7ae1f183b7f0513483e7becda3","tid":126141,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T02:17:28.000Z","msg":"香港邊到有得玩"},{"pid":"cf360e0244087d5f51708759a00269fa4f8ef91b","tid":126141,"uid":82103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T18:15:57.000Z","msg":"賣出未？"},{"pid":"c36c81e5379b049524385cfa636202a400430b3f","tid":126141,"uid":158144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"請問賣左未?"}]}